king its way torwards me. I run into range and whoa it stoped! I start to cast my bolt spell and what does the dam thing do? turn and walk away OUT OF RANGE. then it stops and turns and looks at me. I run into range again and the spider turns and walks out of range again.<br>
<br>
At first I thought this was a freak thing but after hours of hunting them and having hundreds do the same thing over and over again it has to be programed. I found ways around it, pain in the arse Lol. Sprint into range and cast before it gets out or target one and cast then quickly switch to another.<br>
<br>
Now that I think about it, some of the mobs in the plains did this aswell.<br>
<br>
Anyways FYI if your using ranged attacks.<br>
<br>
<br>
Junun<br>
